Skill enhancer: Bard spell
A bard and a fighter make a potent team. The bard can incite a rage in the 
fighter which will enhance the attack capabilities of the fighter. The
fighter and bard must be in the same room when the fighter uses his skill,
because it's the bard who takes the fighter beyond his normal ability. The
berserk increases most of your offensive skills in effectiveness, as well
as reducing the cost to perform some of them.
